                         Tipic Video Library


Details
~~~~~~~

    Version:            0.1a

    Authors:            Francesco Delfino <pluto@tipic.com>
                        Stefano Falsetto <falsetto@gnu.org>

    Homepage:           www.sourceforge.com/projects/tipicforge

    License:            Lesser GPL v2.1 (LGPL)

    Description:        This library provides a portable solution to
			use grab frames from webcam under Linux,
			MacOS X and Windows


